<section class="tools bg-surface-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2>Tools We Use to Automate</h2>
      <p>We build with the best AI tools so your systems are fast, reliable, and smart.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tools-grid" data-animate-stagger>
      <div class="tool-card card">
        <div class="tool-logo">
          <img src="/tools/claude-logo.svg" alt="Claude Code by Anthropic" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="tool-info">
          <h3>Claude Code</h3>
          <p>Anthropic's agentic coding tool. We use Claude Code to build, debug, and deploy your AI systems faster, with the same model powering the intelligence in your automations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card card">
        <div class="tool-logo">
          <img src="/tools/gumloop-logo.svg" alt="Gumloop AI Automation" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="tool-info">
          <h3>Gumloop</h3>
          <p>AI workflow automation platform. We use Gumloop to wire together multi-step automations that handle your lead routing, content generation, screening, and more. All running 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tools {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
  }

  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .tools-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .tool-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .tool-logo {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--bg-surface-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .tool-logo img {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .tool-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs);
  }

  .tool-info p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
